rComments: Great prof, very laid bad atmosphere yet engaging.
Dough is a great teacher. He gives clear instructions on assignments and presentation. I will definitely have his course again!

You can miss class but I don't recommend it, if you miss too much then action will be taken, great prof, easy marker, if you get the material he doesn't add any bidding agenda, pretty straight forward

What he wants for assignments is clear in the sense that he gives you a checklist but when he marks your paper he adds to the checklist. He loves to talk, too much in fact. You are suppose to have read a chapter each class and be prepared to answer questions.
